===2010 census===
The 2010 United States Census counted 5 people in 3 households. Two households consisted of married couples and the third was a male over 65 years of age living alone. The population density was 19.7 per square mile (7.6/km2). The borough contained 3 housing units at an average density of 11.8 per square mile (4.6/km2). All residents were [[White people|white]]. Two residents were aged 25 to 44 and three were older than 65. The median age was 66.3 years.<ref name=Census2010 />

